):

1. *Leda* je sinoć na proslavi pokazala svoju novu haljinu. (She showed her new dress at the party last night.)

2. On se zbog *lede* nije čak ni šminkao. (He didn't even put on makeup because of the frost.)

3. Da li će se *leda* uopšte otopiti do proleća? (Will the frost melt at all until spring?)

4. Pogledaj kako su se *ledali* cvetovi na trgu. (Look how the flowers in the square were frosted.)

5. *Leda* je pokazala svoju najbolju stranu. (The frost showed its best side.)